{
  "stem": "16442.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 379.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And while we were waiting for that, the only way we're able to keep warm-- that we got together, and one body warmed the other.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is how we got a little warmth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after the hanging is finished, then we were able to go back to our barracks and put on our clothes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This happened twice, once when a girl tried to escape and ran to the wires-- which was fully electrified.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as soon as she touched it, the wire pulled her whole body there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they left her there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we had to march by and look at her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they said, this is what happens to everybody who tries to escape.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we knew there was no escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot to mention it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right at the beginning, when we arrived, while we-- we were waiting to take and to work, one day a few SS came and took us out of our barracks, took us over to a big room.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody was hand out cards, postcards with pens.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were supposed to write home, everybody at least two cards, to our relatives to tell them that we are working, and we are very well-treated and well-fed, and everything is just fine.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to give these cards addressed to our relatives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was right at the beginning, because as I mentioned, I was the first transport to Auschwitz from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this obviously had to be sent home before they-- before they brought all the other Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I guess this is how they wanted them to be calm-- that they received our postcards that everything is fine and we are working, which was a big lie.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we did it under the SS fires.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw their baggage.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
